text: Ili jxur DI ili neniam dir gxi ili uttered vort disbelief; ili disbelieved igx submitters. En fakt, ili don up ki ili neniam hav. Ili ribel eben DI His messenger dusx them His grace provisions Ili pent gxi est put them. Sed se ili turn DI testament commit them al painful retribution en this life Hereafter Ili trov ne 1 ter est their lord mastr
